<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1665630-i-have-seen-the-movie-but-so-long-ago-i">I have seen the movie, but so long ago, I only remember the highlights. As far as the book goes, can it be read as a stand-alone, or is it best to read the series?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
