<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/14457828-bren-coombs"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1352580930i/14457828._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/14457828-bren-coombs">Bren Coombs</a>
