<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It&apos;s a good series and adds more depth to the story to read all of it, but this book can stand alone, as well.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It's a good series and adds more depth to the story to read all of it, but this book can stand alone, as well.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
