          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780684853901" href="/book/show/317843.Terms_of_Endearment">review of another edition</a>


          <div>
    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Tatevik is on semi hiatus (trying to finish PHD) by: </span>
      <a href="/user/show/5211606-julie">Julie</a>
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7377638-tatevik-is-on-semi-hiatus-trying-to-finish-phd?shelf=read-in-2021">read-in-2021</a>, 
